      "date": "2013-01-14 18:51:45.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nAndreas,\nYes, this patch almost certainly breaks interop tests with older servers since it looks for new proc variables that didn't even exist in those older versions.  However it is not any more broken than running this test from older versions of the script in old clients on new servers that fail looking from old proc variables that no longer exist in new servers.  I felt it more important to get a fix working for client == server version.  Fully addressing interop problems would need fixes in old versions as well as here.",
